<nav class="breadcrumbs"><a class="homeCrumb" href="http://amazonwatch.org/" title="Amazon Watch home page">Home</a><a class="currentCrumb" href="http://amazonwatch.org/privacy-policy" title="Our Privacy Policy">Our Privacy Policy</a></nav>
<h1>Our Privacy Policy</h1>

</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="large-12 columns content">
<p>Amazon Watch is committed to preserving your privacy and safeguarding your information online. The following statement describes the general information-gathering and -usage practices of our website.</p>
<p>Amazon Watch does not sell or trade names or other personal data that we collect on our website.</p>
<p>Credit card donations through our web site are processed by <a href="http://www.authorize.net/" target="_blank">Authorize.Net</a>. Amazon Watch never receives or stores your credit card information in any format, so there is no risk that it might be hacked or disclosed. We keep a record of your donation and contact information (name, address, etc.) in our database of supporters. </p>
<p>Any bulk mailings we send are clearly identified as being from Amazon Watch and will always include options to unsubscribe and contact us.</p>
<p>We work hard to ensure that your experience on our site is a positive one. If you have any questions about this privacy policy or your dealings with our site, please <a href="about/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
